      • compile

        public DriverAI compile​(CarPanel carPanel)
                 throws java.io.IOException
        Compiles the AI of the given CarPanel if it has not been compiled yet and returns an instance of it. Uses the jOOR library. Uses the get-methods of the CarPanel to get the name of the AI and the name of its file.
        Parameters:
        carPanel - the CarPanel from which the methods gets the required information about the AI.
        Returns:
        an instance of the AI described in the CarPanel given as the parameter.
        Throws:
        java.io.IOException
        See Also:
        DriverAI, CarPanel.getAiName(), CarPanel.getAiFile()
